    <stitle>CAB: 4100, 4200, 4300 AND 4400 MODELS - DESCRIPTION - WINDSHIELD WASHER</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="2">
        <title>WINDSHIELD WASHER</title>
        <para>The windshield washer consists of a washer bottle mounted, motor driven, displacement type pump that
            delivers washer solution to the windshield through hoses and nozzles in the wiper arms. The pump motor (Item
            1) may be integral with washer bottle (Item 2) or removable
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1602605">Figure 5</hotlnk>
